            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:27:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ROG]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ROG Astral GeForce RTX 5090 OC Edition]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[RTX 5090]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288686</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 CES 2025 Nvidia 发布最新 GeForce RTX 50 显示卡系列，而各厂商微调的显示卡产品也陆续推出。ROG(Republic of Gamers) 就发布了最新 OC 版显示卡 ROG Astral GeForce RTX 5090 OC Edition。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288699" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124105947-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124105947-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124105947.jpg 1043w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><h2 data-pm-slice="1 1 []">创新冷却系统</h2><p>全新 Quad-Fan Force 四风扇设计，大幅提升气流与压力达 20%，结合专利 Vapor Chamber 技术与相变 GPU 散热垫，显著降低 GPU 温度。经过精心改良的散热鳍片间距与 MaxContact 热传导技术，确保散热效率提升 10%，让装置在高效运作时依然保持低温稳定。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288689 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110113-694x294.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="294" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110113-694x294.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110113-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288696 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110245-694x393.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="393" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110245-694x393.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110245-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>强化结构与保护</h2><p>显示卡采用全金属铸造框架与背板，搭配 GPU Guard 技术固定 GPU 四角，提供稳固结构与持久保护。PCB 防护涂层进一步抵御湿气、灰尘与杂质，减少短路风险。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288688 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/20250124110027-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-