        </item>
        <item>
            <title>ChatGPT Operator 杀手级 AI 助理登场，自动订位、Claim 钱、Call Uber</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/openai-operator-tool/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=openai-operator-tool</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/openai-operator-tool/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 07:30:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Operator]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288570</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OpenAI 稍早前推出名为 Operator 的人工智能工具，透过模拟人类操作网页方式，自动完成预订、购物及提交资料等日常网络任务。现时仅供美国 ChatGPT Pro 用户使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288571" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat.jpg 854w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CSE77wAdDLg">OpenAI@YouTube</a></p><p>Operator 采用最新 Computer-Using Agent（CUA）人工智能模型，结合 GPT-4o 的视觉功能与推理能力，能准确点击网页按钮、输入文字及选择不同选项，为用户预订餐厅、建立购物清单及报销。OpenAI 已与 Instacart、Uber 和 eBay 等企业合作，加强 Operator 的实用性和功能贴近用户需求。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1288573 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-2.jpg 854w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CSE77wAdDLg">OpenAI@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288577" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-3.jpg 854w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CSE77wAdDLg">OpenAI@YouTube</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1288579" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/introductiontooperat-4.jpg 854w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CSE77wAdDLg">OpenAI@YouTube</a></p><p>尽管 Operator 展现自动化网络任务的强大潜力，但其功能的可用性及潜在风险问题仍不容忽视。为解决问题，Operator 采用三层保护措施，确保用户的使用安全和私隐。</p><p>第一层保护让用户可随时接管操作。例如，当需要输入敏感资讯（如付款资料或登入帐密）时，用户可接手操作，而 Operator 不会收集或截图相关行为。此外，在进行最终步骤或重大操作（如提交订单或发送电邮）前，用户需确认才能执行。同时，Operator 已训练拒绝执行敏感或高风险任务，包括银行交易、重大决策和购买枪械等。</p><p>第二层保护集中于数据私隐管理。如果用户在 ChatGPT 设定中关闭「为所有人改善模型」功能，所有数据将不会用于训练 OpenAI 模型。此外用户亦可透过隐私设定一键删除浏览数据、登入资讯和对话内容，全面掌控个人数据。</p><p>第三层保护则专注于任务执行的安全性。专用的监控模型会即时检测可疑行为或进入高风险网站，必要时可暂停相关任务。系统结合自动与手动审核流程，快速识别新威胁并更新防护措施，进一步提升安全保障。</p><p>ChatGPT Operator 现时仅供美国 ChatGPT Pro 用户使用，其他订阅方案及国家的用户暂时无法体验。不过，OpenAI 已承诺将来会扩展至 Plus、Team 和 Enterprise 用户，但尚未公布具体时间。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://openai.com/index/introducing-operator/">OpenAI</a>、<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2025/01/23/technology/openai-operator-launch.html">New York Times</a></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 倾倾科技背后黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/openai-operator-tool/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《刺客教条：暗影者》开放预购，登上 PS5、PC、Xbox X/S 等平台</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=assassins-creed-shadows-3</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 06:30:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Assassin's Creed Shadows]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1288597</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Ubisoft 宣布《刺客教条》系列全新作品《刺客教条：暗影者》现已开放预购，并将于 3 月 20 日全球同步推出。预购玩家将可免费获得「淡路猎爪」扩充内容，该内容包含新地区、新技能以及超过 10 小时的额外游戏时间。游戏将登陆 PlayStation 5、Xbox Series X|S、配备 Apple 晶片的 Mac（Mac App Store）、Windows PC（包括 Ubisoft Store、Steam、Epic Games Store）和 Amazon Luna 平台。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288617 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_embargo_keyart_-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288601" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_147_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288602 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_149_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>穿越至 16 世纪日本的史诗冒险</h2><p>由 Ubisoft 魁北克工作室主导开发的《刺客教条：暗影者》，将玩家带入 16 世纪的日本，探索忍术专家伊贺女刺客奈绪江和传奇武士弥助之间错综复杂的故事。在这片动荡的土地上，两位主角将在日本统一的历史进程中与大名织田信长的野心正面交锋。游戏的剧情预告片揭示了两人如何在内忧外患的背景下，共同开创新教条的未来。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1288600" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_113_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_164_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_165_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_166_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>多版本选择与专属内容</h2><p>《刺客教条：暗影者》将推出标准版、数码豪华版及典藏版，满足不同玩家需求：</p><ul><li><strong>数码豪华版</strong>：包含游戏主程式、「赤龙双组合包」（包括奈绪江和弥助的专属装备与武器）、「赤龙藏身处组合包」（提供藏身处外观）以及「精通点数」。</li><li><strong>典藏版</strong>：除豪华版数码内容外，还包括实体收藏品，如 Steelbook 铁盒、世界地图、奈绪江与弥助公仔、武士刀刀镡、壁挂教条卷轴、76 页艺术图集及两幅水墨画印刷作品。</li></ul><h2>预购福利：免费扩充内容与专属任务</h2><p>预购任何版本的玩家将可免费获得将于 2025 年稍后推出的「淡路猎爪」扩充内容。这项 DLC 增加全新开放区域，带来更多游戏时间、新技能和装备。奈绪江更将获得新武器「棒」（Bō），协助对抗淡路岛上的危险势力「山贼派」。此外，预购玩家还可解锁专属任务「狗命坎坷」，该任务将于游戏发售时提供。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_172_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_181_screenshot_.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_naoe_kick_t-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1288611" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/acsh_coa_vista.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/24/assassins-creed-shadows-3/game-channel/">《刺客教条：暗影者》开放预购，登上 PS5、PC、Xbox X/S 等平台</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
